FREE DEMO of RogueGods:
A deck-building roguelite for VR & MR where every card transforms into a weapon you wield, a spell, a power, or even an ally. Build your deck, combine magic rings, and ascend Olympus.

Features
Build a living deck:**

On each run discover hundreds of cards to add to your build. 
Choose wisely and create unstoppable synergies to crush your enemies.
